{"tid":1867191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【書生論政】李文亮係藍絲係主要敵人，邪惡政權及其爪牙鷹犬只係次要敵人","createTime":"2020-02-07T05:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T06:00:34.000Z","uid":243790,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b995254d4efec873473f0d93500f8d155677cf","tid":1867191,"uid":243790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔是咪ON9？俾張死光最好嘅圖，同19才子嘅舊文洗腦，咁白痴嘅風向都睇唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次終於出現支爆端倪，仲唔去輸出革命更待何時？有人係咁吹風為乜？因為佢哋好撚驚呀！邪惡政權及其爪牙鷹犬先係主要敵人呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「統一戰線」<br />\n為了實現各個時期特定的戰略目標和任務，同各階級、階層、政黨及一切可能團結的力量，在一定的共同目標下結成的政治聯盟。概括起來，就是「聯合次要敵人，打擊主要敵人」。<br />\n<br />\n「誰是主要敵人？」<br />\n邪惡政權。其爪牙鷹犬次之。<br />\n<br />\n「如何統一戰線？」<br />\n要擴大己方陣營，鞏固革命成果，擊敗邪惡政權。己方必須在革命中使其他社會階層、陣營如中立撚、淺藍絲、民族資產階級等加入己方，或者支持己方的政策，或者最少保持中立，以最大程度孤立敵人&mdash;&mdash;邪惡政權及其爪牙鷹犬。<br />\n<br />\n「屌藍絲得唔得？」<br />\n實行又聯合又鬥爭的基本策略原則。對於統一戰線中的同盟者有聯合，有批評﹔對於各種不同的同盟者有各種不同性質的聯合，有各種不同的批評。聯合藍絲只是為了打擊邪惡政權，所以聯合可以只是過渡性、階段性的。"},{"pid":"e28898bcd07a0ee313527764b65605bbcb92905a","tid":1867191,"uid":345840,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"無錯，主次要分明<br />\n從內部推動支爆"},{"pid":"1be11980e340689c1564ea127e7a8625cdab0bbf","tid":1867191,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7aoTCVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7aoTCVa.jpg&h=b2e520d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e4d9f6b9ff89fdf466e03b0e0c954f4afd81d58","tid":1867191,"uid":243790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1be11980e340689c1564ea127e7a8625cdab0bbf","tid":1867191,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7aoTCVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7aoTCVa.jpg&h=b2e520d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"快撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b2ca9c6e9c29151e18e8b9516b671c2d28b496","tid":1867191,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:58:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推推推推<br />\n全推加速主義</span>"},{"pid":"19b9805464b21017be55f33b2de4113601fe8d22","tid":1867191,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"醫護<br />\n<br />\n投票時間至1600🟥<br />\n<br />\n要6000會員投票呀‼️‼️‼️‼️<br />\n快啲出黎啦‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【延長醫護罷工計劃投票】<br />\n投票截至今日下午四時<br />\n只限會員<br />\n￼<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw%2Fviewform&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=3b1234ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw/viewform</a>"}]}